function strjoinv(separator: String, str_array: String): String {
    // Gjs wrapper for g_strjoinv()
}
  </code></synopsis>
  <p>Joins a number of strings together to form one long string, with the
optional <code>separator</code> inserted between each of them. The returned string
should be freed with <link xref="GLib.free"/>.</p>

<terms>
<item>
<title><code>separator</code></title>
  <p>a string to insert between each of the
    strings, or <code>null</code></p>
</item>
<item>
<title><code>str_array</code></title>
  <p>a <code>null</code>-terminated array of strings to join</p>
